headline: Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade viewership continues to grow
summary: The Macy's (M) Thanksgiving Day Parade has been a holiday staple for generations of Americans as they prep for the big turkey day. With tens of millions of American tuning in to watch every year, viewership is still growing for the event. Yahoo Finance anchor Julie Hyman runs through Macy's reported streaming rights negotiations with NBC, which is owned by Comcast (CMCSA). To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Asking for a Trend here. This post was written by Luke Carberry Mogan.
